382
00:18:10,436 --> 00:18:11,557
I thought if I worked harder,

383
00:18:11,917 --> 00:18:12,956
my Soul Power would have a breakthrough.

384
00:18:14,637 --> 00:18:15,196
But when I realized

385
00:18:15,196 --> 00:18:16,757
