416
00:19:23,517 --> 00:19:24,836
I'm afraid I couldn't hold on.

417
00:19:28,157 --> 00:19:29,757
Wu and I will continue to support you.

418
00:19:31,517 --> 00:19:33,277
Thank you, Master.

419
00:19:35,436 --> 00:19:36,716
